OL,6,FDetective Inspector Matt Marston said:
OL,7,F"This was a complex and protracted
OL,8,Finvestigation. Aslam and Nazir were
OL,9,Fdetermined to take revenge following a
OL,10,Ffall out where they were injured.J"The
OL,11,Flengths they went to in trying to make
OL,12,Fsure they weren't implicated in
OL,13,Fpulling the trigger are immense.
OL,14,F"However, thanks to some great police
OL,15,Fwork and support from our Derbyshire
OL,16,Fcolleagues we were able to place them
OL,17,Ffirmly in the middle of the attempted
OL,18,Fmurder plot.J"We hope that today,
OL,19,Fafter a number of years unravelling
OL,20,Fthis investigation, justice has been
OL,21,Fserved".
